This paper involves the use of artificial intelligence to assist novice players in MOBA games, which falls under the category of AI. It also deals with game theory and player behavior, which can be categorized under GT. The use of machine learning algorithms to analyze player performance falls under LG. The paper also discusses the interaction between the player and the AI agent, which can be categorized under HC. Finally, the paper deals with the use of technology to improve the gaming experience, which can be categorized under CY.
